//about page About Us Welcome to the Community Helping Hands Center! At our center we have plenty of food for you and your family free of price. We know that food insecurity is a real issue that affects many individuals and families in our community. Thats why we’re dedicated to providing a safe and welcoming space where people in need can come and get the food they need to thrive.\n \nOur app is designed to help connect people in need with the resources they require. It allows you to see what we have to food we have to offer to those who need it and calculates how much for every individual in your household. You can easily search for the resources you need and get directions to the nearest location. You can also call or email us to speak to someone for assistance.\n \nWe believe that everyone deserves access to healthy and nutritious food, regardless of their income or circumstances. That’s why we work hard to provide plenty of healthy high quality food options, including options for those who have food allergies. From whole grains to fresh produce to canned goods, we have everything you need to stay healthy.\n \nSo come down to our donation center and see what we have to offer, our friendly staff are always here to help, and we’re committed to having a positive difference in our community.
